Imports System Imports System.Data Imports System.Data.Common Imports System.IO Imports System.Collections.Generic Imports System.Globalization Imports System.Linq Imports Microsoft.VisualBasic Imports System.Windows.Forms Imports OneStream.Shared.Common Imports OneStream.Shared.Wcf Imports OneStream.Shared.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Database Imports OneStream.Stage.Engine Imports OneStream.Stage.Database Imports OneStream.Finance.Engine Imports OneStream.Finance.Database
Namespace OneStream.BusinessRule.Finance.CMD_PGM_Main_Calc Public Class MainClass Public Function Main(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
Select Case api.FunctionType
Case Is = FinanceFunctionType.CustomCalculate
#Region "RollFwdReq: Roll Forward Requirements" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("RollFwdReq") Then
Me.RollFwdReq(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank") Then Me.CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank(si, globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "ReapplyInflation" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ReapplyInflation") Then Me.ReapplyInflation(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyAmount" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyAmount") Then Me.CopyAmount(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyManpower" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyManpower") Then Me.CopyManpower(si,globals,api,args) Return Nothing End If #End Region
#Region "CopyApprovedAmtADM" If args.CustomCalculateArgs.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("CopyApprovedAmtADM") Then Dim calScript As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs("calScript") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"args calScript = " & calScript) api.Data.Calculate(calScript,True) End If #End Region
End Select
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function
'END MAIN =================================================================================================
#Region "Constants" Public REQ_Member_Lists As New OneStream.BusinessRule.Finance.REQ_Member_Lists.MainClass Private BR_REQDataSet As New OneStream.BusinessRule.DashboardDataSet.REQ_DataSet.MainClass Private BR_REQ_String_Helper As New OneStream.BusinessRule.DashboardStringFunction.REQ_String_Helper.MainClass #End Region
#Region "RollFwdReq: Roll Forward Requirements" '----------------------------- ' Purpose: Copy selected Current Year requiremnts to Next Year ' ' LOGIC OVERVIEW: ' - Get list of All requirements ' - Reduce list to only selected requirements(REQ_RollFwd_Status = yes) and in current data unit ' - loop thru list of requirements for accounts = REQ_Copy_List.base ' - copy annotations and amounts from source S#T# to target S#T# ' NOTE: data mgmt controls loop of data units you can write to so we loop through target and get data from source ' ' Usage: ' - From Data Mgmt: ' custom calculate Step --> Business Rule = REQ_Main_Calc & Function Name = RollFwdReq ' ' MODIFIED: ' <date> <user id> <JIRA ticket> <change description> ' 2024-03-26 AK RMW-1171 created ' 2024-09-04 AK RMW-15 modified copy to handle 5 years of annual data and a different account list = REQ_Copy_List --> REQ_Rollover_List ' '----------------------------- Public Function RollFwdReq(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try '========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "REQ_Main_Calc" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "RollFwdReq"
Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sCurrScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim iCurrScenarioYear As Integer = Strings.Right(sCurrScenario,4).XFConvertToInt Dim iPriorScenarioYear As Integer = iCurrScenarioYear - 1 Dim sPriorScenario As String = sCurrScenario.Replace(iCurrScenarioYear.ToString, iPriorScenarioYear.ToString)
Dim sCurrTime As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim iCurrTime As Integer = Strings.Left(sCurrTime,4).XFConvertToInt
Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sTgtMbrScript As String = ""
Dim sPOVEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: sPOVEntity=" & sPOVEntity & " sCurrScenario=" & sCurrScenario & " sCurrTime=" & sCurrTime & " sPriorScenario=" & sPriorScenario & " iPriorScenarioYear=" & iPriorScenarioYear)
'------------------------------------- ' Get All Req E#F# List from prior year '------------------------------------- '!!!!! DVLP NOTE: need to tell GetAllREQList() to use prior scenario and prior year !!!!! args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("EntityMbrFilter", "E#" & sPOVEntity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("TimeOffset", "Prior") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnDim", "E#F#U1#U2#U3#U4#U5#U6#") Dim lsReqAllList As List(Of String) = REQ_Member_Lists.GetAllREQListRollover(si, globals, api, args) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: lsReqAllList count=" & lsReqAllList.Count & " List =" & String.Join(", ", lsReqAllList))
If lsReqAllList.Count = 0 Then Return lsReqAllList
'!!!!! DVLP NOTE: reminder that you can only write to the open data unit at current POV Entity.Time ' therefore the data mgmt job needs to loop thru all enities that may exist in the REQ list
'------------------------------------- ' Reduce list to where roll status <> no and Entity equals POV Entity '------------------------------------- Dim lsRollFwdList As New List(Of String) For Each sRollFwdMbrScript As String In lsReqAllList 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: sRollFwdMbrScript=" & sRollFwdMbrScript) Dim sEntity As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(1).Split("]")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(2).Split("]")(0) Dim sU1 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(3).Split("]")(0) Dim sU2 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(4).Split("]")(0) Dim sU3 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(5).Split("]")(0) Dim sU4 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(6).Split("]")(0) Dim sU5 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(7).Split("]")(0) Dim sU6 As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Split("[")(8).Split("]")(0)
'----- only include REQ for the entity we are at ----- If Not sEntity.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(sPOVEntity) Then Continue For
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: sEntity=" & sEntity & " sFlow=" & sFlow & " sU1=" & sU1 & " sU2=" & sU2 & " sU3=" & sU3 & " sU4=" & sU4 & " sU5=" & sU5 & " sU6=" & sU6)
'----- get rollfwd status ----- sSrcMbrScript = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sPriorScenario & ":T#" & iPriorScenarioYear.ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_RollFwd_Status:I#None:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim sRollFwdStatus As String = api.data.GetDataCellEx(sSrcMbrScript).DataCellAnnotation 'BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: SrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript & " sRollFwdStatus=" & sRollFwdStatus)
If Not sRollFwdStatus.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("no") Then
If lsRollFwdList.Count = 0 Then lsRollFwdList.Add("E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6) Else lsRollFwdList.Add(", E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6) End If
End If
Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: lsRollFwdList Count=" & lsRollFwdList.Count)
'----- exit if no requirements ----- If lsRollFwdList.Count = 0 Then Return lsRollFwdList
Select Case iCurrTime Case iCurrScenarioYear
'====================================================================================================== ' Copy Annotations '======================================================================================================
'------------------------------------- ' get list of accounts to copy in first year of current scenario '------------------------------------- Dim mbrAcctList As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, "A_REQ_Main","A#REQ_Copy_List.base", True) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQ_Main_Calc.RollFwdReq: Account List Count=" & mbrAcctList.Count)
'------------------------------------- ' loop thru reqs within data unit '------------------------------------- For Each sRollFwdMbrScript As String In lsRollFwdList Dim sEntity As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("E#", "~").Split("~")(1).Split(":")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sRollFwdMbrScript.Replace("F#", "~").Split("~")(1).Split(":")(0)
''+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 'Dim tStart As DateTime = Date.Now() ''+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
' '--------*********************** Clear********************---------------------------- ' Dim params As New Dictionary(Of String, String) ' params.Add("Entity", "E#" & sEntity) ' params.Add("Scenario", sCurrScenario) ' params.Add("Flow", sFlow) ' 'params.Add("Time", "T#2023,T#2024,T#2025,T#2026,T#2027,T#2028,T#2029")' & iCurrTime) ' params.Add("Time", "T#" & iCurrTime -1 & ",T#" & iCurrTime & ",T#" & iCurrTime + 1 & ",T#" & iCurrTime + 2 & ",T#" & iCurrTime + 3 & ",T#" & iCurrTime + 4 )' & iCurrTime)
' BRApi.Utilities.ExecuteDataMgmtSequence(si, "Delete_REQ", params)
'api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sCurrScenario & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True)

#Region "CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank" 'Update EH 090324 RMW-1565 Changed REQTime to annual for centralized text update Private Function CalculateWeightedScoreAndRank(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim WFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim WFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim REQTime As String = WFYear Dim sInternalRank As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("InternalRank") Dim sFundCenter As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FundCenter")
'Get cat and weight Dim priCatNameAndWeight As Dictionary(Of String, Decimal) = New Dictionary(Of String, Decimal) priCatNameAndWeight = Me.GetCategoryAndWeight(si, args)
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "REQList = " & REQList.Count) Dim catScoreMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#EEEE" & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" & sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#UUUU:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim REQScores As List(Of REQ_Score) = New List(Of REQ_Score) ' For Each REQ As String In REQList Dim dt As DataTable = BRApi.Utilities.GetSessionDataTable(si,si.UserName,"REQListCVResult")
'Loops For Each row As DataRow In dt.Rows Dim cleanREQ_Entity = row("EntityFlow").Split(":")(0).Replace("e#[","").Replace("]","") Dim cleanREQ_Id = row("EntityFlow").Split(":")(1).Replace("f#[","").Replace("]","") ' Dim cleanREQ_Id As String = REQ.Substring(REQ.IndexOf("f#[") + 3, 6) Dim REQInfo As REQ_Score = New REQ_Score REQInfo.REQ_Id = cleanREQ_Id ' Dim cleanREQ_Entity As String = REQ.Split(":"c)(0).Split("["c)(1).Trim("]"c) REQInfo.REQ_Entity = cleanREQ_Entity REQInfo.scores = New Dictionary(Of String, Decimal)
For Each kp As KeyValuePair(Of String, Decimal) In priCatNameAndWeight 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, wfProfileName) 'replace key for EEEE, UUUU and FFFF and get score. Also get the weight from the key and calculate the total Weighted score Dim priCatScore As Decimal = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, catScoreMemScript.Replace("EEEE",cleanREQ_Entity ).Replace("UUUU",kp.Key).Replace("FFFF",cleanREQ_Id)).DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "pricatScore = " & pricatScore) If (priCatScore > 0) Then REQInfo.scores.Add(kp.Key, priCatScore) REQInfo.totalWeightedScore += priCatScore * (kp.Value/100) End If Next
'Add the REQ class to the list REQScores.Add(REQInfo) Next 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Here") 'Sort the REQs REQScores = REQScores.OrderByDescending(Function(u) u.totalWeightedScore).ToList
'Update the REQ with the calculated weight
Dim rank As Integer = 0 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sFundcenter = " & sFundCenter) For Each REQScore As REQ_Score In REQScores Dim SaveTotalScoreMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & REQScore.REQ_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Score:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim SaveRankMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & REQScore.REQ_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Calc_Rank:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim SaveOverrideMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & REQScore.REQ_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Override_Rank:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim SaveInternalRankMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & REQScore.REQ_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Internal_Rank:F#FFFF:O#BeforeAdj:I#" &sFundCenter & ":U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
'Update REQ Status to Prioritize Dim REQStatusMemberScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & REQScore.REQ_Entity & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Rqmt_Status:F#" & REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper() & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim REQStatus As String = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, REQStatusMemberScript).DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation Dim CurrentLevel As String = REQStatus.Substring(0,2) Dim NewStatus As String = CurrentLevel & " Prioritized"
Dim objListofScriptsWFStatus As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValWFStatus As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValWFStatus.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValWFStatus.Script = REQStatusMemberScript objScriptValWFStatus.TextValue = NewStatus objScriptValWFStatus.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsWFStatus.Add(objScriptValWFStatus)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsWFStatus)
rank = rank + 1
Dim objListofScriptsTotalScore As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValTotalScore As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValTotalScore.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValTotalScore.Script = SaveTotalScoreMemScript.Replace("FFFF", REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValTotalScore.Amount = REQScore.totalWeightedScore objScriptValTotalScore.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsTotalScore.Add(objScriptValTotalScore)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsTotalScore)
Dim objListofScriptsRank As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValRank As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValRank.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValRank.Script = SaveRankMemScript.Replace("FFFF", REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValRank.Amount = rank objScriptValRank.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsRank.Add(objScriptValRank)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsRank)
Dim objListofScriptsOverride As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValOverride As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValOverride.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValOverride.Script = SaveOverrideMemScript.Replace("FFFF", REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValOverride.Amount = rank objScriptValOverride.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsOverride.Add(objScriptValOverride)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsOverride)
If sInternalRank.XFContainsIgnoreCase("True") Then
Dim objListofScriptsInternal As New List(Of MemberScriptandValue) Dim objScriptValInternal As New MemberScriptAndValue objScriptValInternal.CubeName = WFCube objScriptValInternal.Script = SaveInternalRankMemScript.Replace("FFFF", REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper()) objScriptValInternal.Amount = rank objScriptValInternal.IsNoData = False objListofScriptsInternal.Add(objScriptValInternal)
BRApi.Finance.Data.SetDataCellsUsingMemberScript(si, objListofScriptsInternal) End If 'set last updated name and date, and update status history Dim BR_REQ_SolutionHelper As New OneStream.BusinessRule.DashboardExtender.REQ_SolutionHelper.MainClass Dim deArgs As New DashboardExtenderArgs deArgs.FunctionType = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged deArgs.FunctionName = "LastUpdated" deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("updatedREQEntity", REQScore.REQ_Entity) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("updatedREQFlow", REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper()) BR_REQ_SolutionHelper.Main(si, globals, api, deArgs)
deArgs.FunctionType = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged deArgs.FunctionName = "UpdateStatusHistory" deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ufrEntity", REQScore.REQ_Entity) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ufrFlow", REQScore.REQ_Id.ToUpper()) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("FundCenter", sFundCenter) deArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("status", NewStatus) BR_REQ_SolutionHelper.Main(si, globals, api, deArgs)
Next
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function
'Created 10/15/2023 - YH 'This rule gets the catogery And weight that are configured for a given fund center 'Update EH 090324 RMW-1565 Changed REQTime to annual for centralized text update Private Function GetCategoryAndWeight(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try 'Get the list of catagories Dim WFCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim WFScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim WFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim REQTime As String = WFYear
Dim sFundCenter As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FundCenter") 'Brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"entity = " & REQEntity) Dim priCatMembers As List(Of MemberInfo) Dim priFilter As String = "U5#UFR_Priority_Category.Children" Dim priCatDimPk As DimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U5_Main") priCatMembers = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, priCatDimPk, priFilter, True)
Dim catNameMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sFundCenter & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Name:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#UUUU:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim catWeightMemScript As String = "Cb#" & WFCube & ":E#" & sFundCenter & ":C#Local:S#" & WFScenario & ":T#" & REQTime & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Cat_Weight:F#None:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#UUUU:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim priCatName As String = "" Dim priCatWeight As Decimal
Dim priCatNameAndWeight As Dictionary(Of String, Decimal) = New Dictionary(Of String, Decimal) For Each pricat As MemberInfo In priCatMembers priCatName = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, catNameMemScript.Replace("UUUU",priCat.Member.Name)).DataCellEx.DataCellAnnotation 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "priCatName = " & priCatName) If (Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(priCatName)) Then priCatWeight = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, WFCube, catWeightMemScript.Replace("UUUU",priCat.Member.Name)).DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "priCatWeight = " & priCatWeight) priCatNameAndWeight.Add(priCat.Member.Name, priCatWeight) End If Next
Return priCatNameAndWeight
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function

#Region "ReapplyInflation" Public Function ReapplyInflation(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
'========== routine vars ============================================================================================================ Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim iCurrScenarioYear As Integer = Strings.Right(wfScenarioName,4).XFConvertToInt Dim scbxEntity As String= args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity") Dim sFinalEntity As String = scbxEntity.Replace("_General","") Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim sSrcMbrScriptFilter As String = "" Dim sTgtMbrScript As String = ""
'------------------------------------- ' Get All Req E#F# List '------------------------------------- args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("EntityMbrFilter", sFinalEntity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnDim", "E#F#") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("TitleSearch","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Mode", "Current")
Dim lsReqAllList As List(Of String) = REQ_Member_Lists.GetAllREQListReapplyInflation(si, globals, api, args)
If lsReqAllList.Count = 0 Then Return lsReqAllList
'Reduce list to Entity equals cbx Entity Dim lsreapplylist As New List(Of String) For Each sreapplyMbrScript As String In lsReqAllList
Dim sEntity As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Split("[")(1).Split("]")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Split("[")(2).Split("]")(0)
'----- only include REQ for the entity we are at ----- If Not sEntity.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(sFinalEntity) Then Continue For
'--------- Filter out REQs at L1 and L2 Status --------- sSrcMbrScriptFilter = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & (iCurrScenarioYear).ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScriptFilter &= ":V#Annotation:A#REQ_Rqmt_Status:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:I#None:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#ReadOnlyAnnotation"
Dim sFilterStatus As String = api.data.GetDataCellEx(sSrcMbrScriptFilter).DataCellAnnotation
If sFilterStatus.XFContainsIgnoreCase("L1") Or sFilterStatus.XFContainsIgnoreCase("L2") Then Continue For
If lsreapplylist.Count = 0 Then lsreapplylist.Add("E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow) Else lsreapplylist.Add(", E#" & sEntity & ":F#" & sFlow) End If
Next
'----- exit if no requirements ----- If lsreapplylist.Count = 0 Then Return lsreapplylist
'------------------------------------- ' loop thru reqs within data unit '------------------------------------- For Each sreapplyMbrScript As String In lsreapplylist Dim sEntity As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Replace("E#", "~").Split("~")(1).Split(":")(0) Dim sFlow As String = sreapplyMbrScript.Replace("F#", "~").Split("~")(1).Split(":")(0)
'------------------------------------- ' Clear pre-existing amounts '------------------------------------- 'api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sCurrScenario & ":T#" & & (iCurrScenarioYear+4).ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True)
'--------- copy req amounts --------- sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & (iCurrScenarioYear+3).ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntity sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow & ":O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None)"
Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False)
Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Reapply Inflation: Invalid Soure Requested Amount Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
For Each dcCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sIC As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetICName(api) Dim sU1 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU5 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD5Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api)
Dim sAPPN As String = "" If sU1.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("none") Then sAPPN = "None" Else sAPPN = api.Members.GetParents(BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_APPN_FUND"), api.Members.GetMemberId(dimtypeid.UD1, sU1), True )(0).Name & "_General" End If Dim sInfRateScript As String = "Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & iCurrScenarioYear.ToString & ":C#USD:E#" & wfCube & "_General:V#Periodic:A#PGM_Inflation_Rate_Amt:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:F#None" sInfRateScript &= ":U1#" & sAPPN & ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim dInflationRate As Decimal = 0 Try dInflationRate =api.data.GetDataCellEx(sInfRateScript).DataCell.CellAmount
Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Reapply Inflation: Invalid Inflation Rate Member Script. sInfRateScript=" & sInfRateScript) End Try
Dim dAmt As Decimal = Math.Round(dcCell.CellAmount * (1 + (dInflationRate/100)))
Dim sTgtMbrScriptForm As String = "Cb#" &wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & (iCurrScenarioYear+4).ToString & ":C#Local:E#" & sEntity & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None"& ":I#" & sIC & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6
Dim targetCell As DataCell Dim targetCellInfo As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript targetCellInfo = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, wfCube, sTgtMbrScriptForm) targetCell = targetCellInfo.DataCellEx.DataCell
'Only write Labor Cost to cube if NOT manually inputted by user. If (targetCell.CellStatus.StorageType.ToString <> "Input" Or targetCell.CellStatus.IsRealData <> "True") Then api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dAmt, False, True) End If Next Next
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "CopyAmount" Public Function CopyAmount(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
Dim account As String = "REQ_Requested_Amt" Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim FY As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim trgtEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name Dim trgtScenario As String = api.Pov.Scenario.Name Dim trgtFlow As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("trgtFlow") Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = "" Dim srcEntity As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("srcEntity") Dim srcFlow As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("srcFlow") Dim srcSenario As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("srcSenario") Dim trgtScript As String = "" Dim srcScript As String = "E#" & srcEntity & ":S#" & srcSenario & ":T#" & FY & ":F#" & srcFlow & ":I#" & srcEntity & ":A#" & account trgtScript = "E#" & trgtEntity & ":S#" & trgtScenario & ":T#" & FY & ":F#" & trgtFlow & ":I#" & trgtEntity & ":A#" & account Dim calScript As String = trgtScript & " = " & srcScript
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"trgtScript = " & trgtScript)
api.Data.ClearCalculatedData(trgtScript, True, True, True, True)
api.Data.Calculate(calScript,True)
Return Nothing
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "CopyManpower" 'Updated 12/03/2024 by Fronz - changed BO5 to BOC & added the 'Clear Existing Data' lines of code Public Function CopyManpower(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try Dim sFlow As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("REQ") Dim sEntityGeneral As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity") Dim sSourcePosition As String = args.CustomCalculateArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("SourcePB") Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sTargetScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim sTargetFirstYear As String = sTargetScenario.Trim.Substring(sTargetScenario.Length-4) Dim sTargetYear As String = api.Pov.Time.Name Dim sSrcMbrScript As String = ""
Dim sBOCSourceMbrScript As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & ":C#Local:E#" & sCube & ":V#Periodic:A#BOC:O#BeforeAdj:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top:F#Baseline:U1#Top:U2#Top:U3#Top:U4#Top:U5#Top:U6#Top" Dim BOCSourceCell As String = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(sBOCSourceMbrScript).DataCell.CellAmount Dim sBO6SourceMbrScript As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & ":C#Local:E#" & sCube & ":V#Periodic:A#BO6:O#BeforeAdj:U7#Top:U8#Top:I#Top:F#Baseline:U1#Top:U2#Top:U3#Top:U4#Top:U5#Top:U6#Top" Dim BO6SourceCell As String = api.Data.GetDataCellEx(sBO6SourceMbrScript).DataCell.CellAmount 'Clear existing data api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntityGeneral & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True) api.Data.ClearCalculatedData("Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":C#USD:E#" & sEntityGeneral & ":V#Periodic:A#BO6:F#" & sFlow, True, True, True, True) '--Copy overlapping years for BO6 data-- If Not BO6SourceCell.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(0) Then sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear & ":C#Local:E#" & sCube sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#BO6:F#Baseline:O#BeforeAdj:I#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top)"

Dim dAmt As Decimal = dcCell.CellAmount
Dim sTgtMbrScriptForm As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":E#" & sEntityGeneral & ":C#Local:S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYear & ":V#Periodic:A#BO6:F#" & sFlow & ":O#Forms:I#" & sEntityGeneral & ":U1#" & sU1 & "_General" & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6 & ":U7#None:U8#None"

api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dAmt, False, True)
Next '--Copy missing years for BO6 data-- Else sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear - 1 & ":C#Local:E#" & sCube sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#BO6:F#Baseline:O#BeforeAdj:I#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top)"

Dim dAmt As Decimal = dcCell.CellAmount

api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dAmt, False, True)
Next '--Copy missing years for BOC data-- Else
sSrcMbrScript = "RemoveZeros(Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sSourcePosition & ":T#" & sTargetYear - 1 & ":C#USD:E#" & sCube sSrcMbrScript &= ":V#Periodic:A#BOC:F#Baseline:O#BeforeAdj:I#Top:U7#Top:U8#Top)"
Dim dbFundingLines As DataBuffer = Nothing Try dbFundingLines = api.Data.GetDataBufferUsingFormula(sSrcMbrScript,,False) Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Reapply Inflation: Invalid Soure Member Script. sSrcMbrScript=" & sSrcMbrScript) End Try
For Each dcCell As DataBufferCell In dbFundingLines.DataBufferCells.values Dim sIC As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetICName(api) Dim sU1 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD1Name(api) Dim sU2 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD2Name(api) Dim sU3 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD3Name(api) Dim sU4 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD4Name(api) Dim sU5 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD5Name(api) Dim sU6 As String = dcCell.DataBufferCellPk.GetUD6Name(api)
Dim sInfRateScript As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetFirstYear & ":C#USD:E#" & sCube & "_General" & ":V#Periodic:A#PGM_Inflation_Rate_Amt:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:F#None" sInfRateScript &= ":U1#" & sU1 & "_General" & ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None"
Dim dInflationRate As Decimal = 0 Try dInflationRate = api.data.GetDataCellEx(sInfRateScript).DataCell.CellAmount
Catch ex As Exception Throw New System.Exception( "Apply Inflation: Invalid Inflation Rate Member Script. sInfRateScript=" & sInfRateScript) End Try
Dim dAmt As Integer = dcCell.CellAmount * (1 + (dInflationRate/100)) 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"origamt=" & dcCell.CellAmount & ": inflate=" & dInflationRate & "inflate/100+1=" & (1 + (dInflationRate/100)) & "damt=" & dAmt) Dim sTgtMbrScriptForm As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sTargetScenario & ":T#" & sTargetYear & ":C#Local:E#" & sEntityGeneral & ":V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:O#Forms:U7#None:U8#None"& ":I#" & sEntityGeneral & ":F#" & sFlow & ":U1#" & sU1 & "_General" & ":U2#" & sU2 & ":U3#" & sU3 & ":U4#" & sU4 & ":U5#" & sU5 & ":U6#" & sU6
Dim targetCell As DataCell Dim targetCellInfo As DataCellInfoUsingMemberScript targetCellInfo = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sTgtMbrScriptForm) targetCell = targetCellInfo.DataCellEx.DataCell
'Only write Labor Cost to cube if NOT manually inputted by user. If (targetCell.CellStatus.StorageType.ToString <> "Input" Or targetCell.CellStatus.IsRealData <> "True") Then api.Data.SetDataCell(api.Data.GetDataCell(targetCell.DataCellPk).DataCellPk.CreateMemberScriptBuilder(api).GetMemberScript, dAmt, False, True) End If

Imports System Imports System.Data Imports System.Data.Common Imports System.IO Imports System.Collections.Generic Imports System.Globalization Imports System.Linq Imports Microsoft.VisualBasic Imports System.Windows.Forms Imports OneStream.Shared.Common Imports OneStream.Shared.Wcf Imports OneStream.Shared.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Database Imports OneStream.Stage.Engine Imports OneStream.Stage.Database Imports OneStream.Finance.Engine Imports OneStream.Finance.Database

Namespace OneStream.BusinessRule.Finance.CMD_PGM_Mbr_Lists Public Class MainClass ' Public Sub New() ' Function CreateProperty ' Property financeArgs As New FinanceRulesArgs ' End Sub Public Function Main(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As Object Try
'========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "REQ_Member_Lists" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "Main"

#Region "GetREQ_IC" '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ' Created: 2023-Oct-10 - AK ' ' Purpose: return IC for a given FundCenter based on the L# we are at ' ' Invocation: MAIN() args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetREQ_IC") ' ' Usage Instructions from a cube view: ' E#Root.CustomMemberList(BRName=REQ_Member_Lists, MemberListName=GetREQ_IC) ' ' Where: ' ' Usage Instructions from a rule: ' ' ' Dim sIC As MemberInfo = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,api.pov.EntityDim.DimPk,"E#Root.CustomMemberList(BRName=REQ_Member_Lists, MemberListName=GetREQ_IC) ' ' 'Modifications: '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Public Function GetREQ_IC(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As String '(Commented temporary Try
'========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "GetREQ_IC"
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== workflow vars ========================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim wfScenarioTypeID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetScenarioType(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey).Id Dim wfTimeName As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) ' Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) ' Dim iWFMonth As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetMonthIdFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
Dim sIC As String = ""
' If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("CMD") Then
' Else
' End If
'Get workflow level Dim sWFLevel As String = wfProfileName.Substring(1,1) 'BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "sWFLevel = " & sWFLevel) Dim iWFLevel As String = CInt(sWFLevel) Dim sMode As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs("Mode")
Select Case True Case sMode.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Curr") 'do nothing Case sMode.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Prior")
iWFLevel = iWFLevel + 1 Case Else Throw New System.Exception("GetREQ_IC(): Invalid Mode = " & sMode ) End Select
'Get Fund Center Level Dim sFundCenter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs("FundCenter") Dim MemberFC As Member = api.Members.GetMember(dimtype.Entity.Id, sFundCenter) Dim EntDimPK As DimPk = api.Dimensions.GetDim("E_Army").DimPk Dim sFundCenterLevel As String = api.Entity.Text(MemberFC.MemberId, 3) 'Dim iFundCenterLevel As Integer = CInt(sFundCenterLevel.Split("=")(1).Replace("L","")) Dim iFundCenterLevel As Integer = CInt(sFundCenterLevel.Split("=")(1)) 'BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "GetREQ_IC: MemberFC=" & MemberFC.Name & " sMode=" & sMode & " sFundCenterLevel=" & sFundCenterLevel & " iFundCenterLevel=" & iFundCenterLevel & " sWFLevel=" & sWFLevel & " iWFLevel=" & iWFLevel) 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si," Case WF LEvel = " & iFundCenterLevel - iWFLevel) Select Case iFundCenterLevel - iWFLevel
Case -1 sIC = "None" Case 0 sIC = sFundCenter Case 1 sIC = api.Members.GetParents(EntDimPK,MemberFC.MemberId,False)(0).Name & "_General" Case 2 sIC = api.Members.GetParents(EntDimPK,MemberFC.MemberId,False)(0).Name Dim dimICID As Member = api.Members.GetMember(dimtype.Entity.Id,sIC) sIC = api.Members.GetParents(EntDimPK,dimICID.MemberId,False)(0).Name & "_General" Case 3 sIC = api.Members.GetParents(EntDimPK,MemberFC.MemberId,False)(0).Name Dim dimICID As Member = api.Members.GetMember(dimtype.Entity.Id,sIC) sIC = api.Members.GetParents(EntDimPK,dimICID.MemberId,False)(0).Name dimICID = api.Members.GetMember(dimtype.Entity.Id,sIC) sIC = api.Members.GetParents(EntDimPK,dimICID.MemberId,False)(0).Name & "_General" Case Else Throw New System.Exception("GetREQ_IC(): Fund Center Level variance is -1 > x > 3") End Select
Return sIC
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "GetREQRankedList()" '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ' Created: 2023-Oct-10 - AK ' ' Purpose: return list of REQ members orederd by rank and unranked REQs are appended to the end of the list ' ' Invocation: MAIN() args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("GetREQPriorityList") ' ' Usage Instructions from a cube view: ' E#Root.CustomMemberList(BRName=REQ_Member_Lists, MemberListName=GetREQPriorityList, DimDef=E#F#, Entity=|WFCube|.base, Flow=Command_Requirements.base , EntityFilter= ) ' ' Where: ' DimDef= is a string of the dimensions you want returned ' ' Entity= can be a member( A5766 ) or a list( [A5766,A57XX] ) or a member expansion( TRADOC.base ) ' ' Flow= can be a member( REQ_01 ) or a list( [REQ_01,REQ_02] ) or a member expansion( Command_Requirements.base ) ' ' EntityFilter: ' NOTE: consider using bound parameter from a single select or mulitselect combobox ( i.e. EntityFilter=|!paramFundCenter!| ) ' NOTE: code will append member or list as a filter ' EntityFilter can be a member( A5766 ) or a list( [A5766,A57XX] ' ' Usage Instructions from a rule: ' ' ' Dim sEntity As String = api.Pov.Entity.Name ' ' Dim objMbrInfoList As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si,api.pov.EntityDim.DimPk,"E#Root.CustomMemberList(BRName=REQ_Member_Lists, MemberListName=GetREQPriorityList, DimDef=E#F#, Entity=" & sEntity & ", Flow=Command_Requirements.base, EntityFilter= )",True) ' ' 'Modifications: '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Public Function GetREQRankedList(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try
Dim lsDimMbrs = Me.GetDimMbrsList(si,globals,api,args) If lsDimMbrs Is Nothing Then Return Nothing
Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) 'Dim wfScenarioTypeID As Integer = "48" 'BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetScenarioType(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey).Id Dim wfTimeName As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim sFundCenter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("cbxEntity").Trim
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== loop thru REQs and divide into ranked and unranked lists ==================================================================== '================================================================================================================================================== Dim lsRankedREQList As New List(Of REQ) Dim lsUnrankedREQList As New List(Of String) 'Dim wfLevel As String = wfProfileName.Substring(0,2) For Each sMbrScript As String In lsDimMbrs '--------- get REQ rank --------- Dim sREQRank_Script As String = sMbrScript & ":Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & iWFYear & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Priority_Override_Rank:I#" & sFundCenter & ":O#BeforeAdj:U1#None:U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim dREQRank As Decimal = api.Data.GetDataCell(sREQRank_Script).CellAmount 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,sDebugFuncName & " sREQRank_Script=" & sREQRank_Script & " dREQRank=" & dREQRank) 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Line652") If dREQRank <> 0 Then Dim objREQ As New REQ objREQ.sMbrScript = sMbrScript objREQ.iRank = dREQRank lsRankedREQList.Add(objREQ) Else lsUnrankedREQList.Add(sMbrScript) End If
Next
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Build List") '================================================================================================================================================== '========== build REQ return list ================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim lsREQList As New List(Of String)
'--------- add ranked REQs --------- If lsRankedREQList.Count > 0 Then Dim lsSortedRankedREQList = From objREQ In lsRankedREQList Order By objREQ.iRank For Each objREQ As REQ In lsSortedRankedREQList 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, " objREQ.sMbrScript=" & objREQ.sMbrScript) lsREQList.Add(objREQ.sMbrScript) Next End If 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Line683") '--------- add unranked REQs --------- If lsUnrankedREQList.Count > 0 Then lsREQList.AddRange(lsUnrankedREQList) End If 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Line682") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "lsREQList.Count = " & lsREQList.Count) '================================================================================================================================================== '========== return REQ list ======================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"Exit GetREQRankedList") Return lsREQList Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "Get Dimensional Mbrs List By Status"
Public Function GetDimMbrsList(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try '========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "REQ_Member_Lists" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "GetDimMbrsList"
Dim wfProfileName As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).Name Dim wfCube = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim wfScenarioName As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) 'Dim wfScenarioTypeID As Integer = "48" 'BRApi.Finance.Scenario.GetScenarioType(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey).Id Dim wfTimeName As String = BRApi.Finance.Time.GetNameFromId(si,si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim iWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim iWFMonth As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetMonthIdFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey) Dim BR_REQDataSet As New OneStream.BusinessRule.DashboardDataSet.REQ_DataSet.MainClass 'Passed parameters Dim sDimDef As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ReturnDim").trim Dim sEntityParam As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("cbxEntity").trim Dim sTitleSearch As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TitleSearch", "") Dim sCPA As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CPAFilter", "") Dim sMode As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("mode").trim
'If entity is passed in like .Children when entity is not selected, it is rejeted If sEntityParam.StartsWith(".") Then Return Nothing
'entityList Dim lsRowMbrList As New List(Of String) Dim sCubeView As String = "" sCubeView = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CubeView") Dim lsEntity As New List(Of String) Dim lsFlow As New List(Of String) Dim sEntity As String = "" Dim sFlow As String = ""
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== get REQs based on status using REQ_DataSet ============================================================================================ '================================================================================================================================================== 'Args to pass into dataset BR Dim dsArgs As New DashboardDataSetArgs dsargs.FunctionType = DashboardDataSetFunctionType.GetDataSet dsArgs.DataSetName = "REQListByEntityAndStatus" dsArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", sEntityParam) dsargs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("CubeView", sCubeView) dsargs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("FundCenterPrompt", sEntityParam) dsargs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("TitleSearch", sTitleSearch) dsargs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("CPAFilter", sCPA)
'Call dataset BR to return a datatable that has been filtered by REQ status Dim objDT As New DataTable
objDT = BR_REQDataset.Main(si, globals, api, dsArgs)
If objDT.Rows.Count = 0 Then If sMode = "CVResult" Then Dim dt As New DataTable("REQListCVResult")
Dim objCol = New DataColumn objCol.ColumnName = "EntityFlow" objCol.DataType = GetType(String) objCol.DefaultValue = "" objCol.AllowDBNull = False dt.Columns.Add(objCol) BRApi.Utilities.SetSessionDataTable(si,si.UserName,"REQListCVResult",dt) End If Return Nothing End If
'Loop through datatable to place REQ members into a comma delimited string For Each dtRow As DataRow In objDT.Rows
'Create args for flow parsing XFBR - added RMW-1004 Dim FlowArgs As DashboardStringFunctionArgs = New DashboardStringFunctionArgs FlowArgs.FunctionName="TitleParseFlow" FlowArgs.NameValuePairs.Add("title",dtRow.Item("Value"))
Dim EntityArgs As DashboardStringFunctionArgs = New DashboardStringFunctionArgs EntityArgs.FunctionName="TitleParseEntity" EntityArgs.NameValuePairs.Add("title",dtRow.Item("Value"))
Dim parsedFlow As String = BR_REQ_String_Helper.Main(si, globals, api, FlowArgs) Dim parsedEntity As String = BR_REQ_String_Helper.Main(si, globals, api, EntityArgs)
lsRowMbrList.Add($"E#[{parsedEntity}]:F#[{parsedFlow}]".ToLower) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,$"E#[{parsedEntity}]:F#[{parsedFlow}]") If Not lsEntity.Contains(parsedEntity) Then lsEntity.Add(parsedEntity) End If If Not lsFlow.Contains(parsedFlow) Then lsFlow.Add(parsedFlow) End If
Next
'Check if loop output values If lsRowMbrList.Count = 0 Then Return Nothing Else sEntity = String.Join(",",lsEntity) sFlow = String.Join(",",lsFlow)
'sEntity = "A97AB,A97AC...." 'sFlow = "01,03,..." End If '================================================================================================================================================== '========== get REQs that have data based on Filters using General_Member_lists =================================================================== '==================================================================================================================================================
Dim lsMasterDimList As New List( Of String) If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sDimDef) Then Return lsRowMbrList Else If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#") And sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("F#") Then sDimDef = "E#F#" & sDimDef.Replace("E#","").Replace("F#","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", sDimDef) Else args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#" & sDimDef) End If If wfProfileName.XFContainsIgnoreCase("Rollover") Then iWFYear = iWFYear - 1 wfScenarioName = $"PGM_C{iWFYear}" End If 'Commented by Fronz 09/27/2024 - need to check for data values within FYDP 5 year timeframe rather than current WF year 'Updated 11/5/24 by JM - Updated to add U6# Filter 'Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":T#" & iWFYear & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U6#Top:U7#Top:U8#None" Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#" & wfCube & ":S#" & wfScenarioName & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U7#Top:U8#None" args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Time", iWFYear & ", " & iWFYear+1 & ", " & iWFYear+2 & ", " & iWFYear+3 & ", " & iWFYear+4 ) ' Dim sEntity As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Entity").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", sEntity)
' Dim sFlow As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Flow").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", sFlow) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True") Dim sIC As String = "" If args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.ContainsKey("IC") Then sIC = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("IC").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("IC", sIC) End If
Dim sEntityFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("EntityFilter").trim
Dim FlowFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FlowFilter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(FlowFilter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":F#Command_Requirements.Base" ' args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("EntityFilter", sEntityFilter) Dim U1ParentFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U1ParentFilter").trim Dim U1Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U1Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U1Filter) And String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U1ParentFilter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U1#Top" ' If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U1Filter) Then args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U1Filter", U1Filter)
Dim U2Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U2Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U2Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U2#Top" ' If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U2Filter) Then args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U2Filter", U2Filter)
Dim U3ParentFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U3ParentFilter").trim ' If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3ParentFilter) Then args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U3ParentFilter", U3ParentFilter)
Dim U3Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U3Filter").trim ' If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3Filter) Then args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U3Filter", U3Filter)
If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3Filter) And String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3ParentFilter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U3#Top"
Dim U4Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U4Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U4Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U4#Top" ' If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U4Filter) Then args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("U4Filter", U4Filter) Dim U6Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U6Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U6Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U6#Top"
If args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.ContainsKey("ICFilter") Then Dim sICFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ICFilter").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ICFilter", sICFilter) End If 'BRapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"ent: " & sEntity & " flow: " &sFlow & " IC: " & sIC & "EntityFiler = " & sEntityFilter) lsMasterDimList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args)
End If
Dim lsDimMbrs As New List(Of String) Dim lsCacheDimMbrs As New List(Of String) For Each x As String In lsRowMbrList 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "x= " & x) For Each y As String In lsMasterDimList 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "y= " & y) If y.Contains(x) Then If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#F#") Then lsDimMbrs.Add(y) lsCacheDimMbrs.Add(x) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, y) Else lsDimMbrs.Add(y.Replace($"{x}:","")) End If End If Next Next
If lsDimMbrs.Count = 0 Then Return Nothing lsDimMbrs = lsDimMbrs.Distinct().ToList() lsDimMbrs.Sort()
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== If the cubeview passed in an arg of CVResult, write and cache a data table of the EntityFlow list ===================================== '========== This data table is used to grab the list of 'filtered' requirement for mass submission (validate, prioritication, approve) ============ '========== Data Table is used in REQ_SOlutionHelper ex: ValidateREQS ============================================================================ '================================================================================================================================================== If sMode = "CVResult" Then lsCacheDimMbrs = lsCacheDimMbrs.Distinct().ToList() lsCacheDimMbrs.Sort()
Dim dt As New DataTable("REQListCVResult")
Dim objCol = New DataColumn objCol.ColumnName = "EntityFlow" objCol.DataType = GetType(String) objCol.DefaultValue = "" objCol.AllowDBNull = False dt.Columns.Add(objCol)
For Each item As String In lsCacheDimMbrs Dim row As DataRow = dt.NewRow() row("EntityFlow") = item dt.Rows.Add(row) Next BRApi.Utilities.SetSessionDataTable(si,si.UserName,"REQListCVResult",dt) End If
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== If provided a cache name, cache the list as a string in user session variable (operate in the same principle as GetFilteredDataRow) === '================================================================================================================================================== Dim sCacheName As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("CacheName").Trim If lsDimMbrs.Count = 0 Then BRApi.Utilities.SetWorkspaceSessionSetting(si, si.UserName, "FilteredDataRows", sCacheName, "") Else '----- store row headers to user session variable ----- If sCacheName <> "" Then BRApi.Utilities.SetWorkspaceSessionSetting(si, si.UserName, "FilteredDataRows", sCacheName, String.Join(",",lsDimMbrs)) End If
Return lsDimMbrs Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "GetAllREQList() new" '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ' PURPOSE: return list of all E#F# requirements - searches data attachment table where REQ_Title is not blank ' ' LOGIC OVERVIEW: ' - SQL query against table = DATAATTACHMENT where REQ_Title is not empty ' - return list of E#F# ' ' USAGE: ' - From another rule: ' Public REQ_Member_Lists As New OneStream.BusinessRule.Finance.REQ_Member_Lists.MainClass ' ' args.MemberListArgs = New MemberListArgs ' args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Year", iPriorYear) ' Dim lsReqAllList As List(Of String) = REQ_Member_Lists.GetAllREQList(si, globals, api, args) ' ' MODIFIED: ' <date> <user id> <JIRA ticket> <change description> ' 2024-04-02 AK RMW-1171 created ' 2024-09-03 KN ' 2024-09-23 EH RMW-1732 revert req_shared and updated to return E#None:F#None when empty '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Public Function GetAllREQList(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try
'========== debug vars ============================================================================================================ Dim sDebugRuleName As String = "REQ_Member_Lists" Dim sDebugFuncName As String = "GetAllREQList"
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== workflow vars ========================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sCurrScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim iCurrYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
Dim sTitleScenario As String = sCurrScenario Dim sTitleYear As String = iCurrYear.ToString
Dim lsEntity As New List(Of String) Dim lsFlow As New List(Of String)
Dim scbxEntity As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("cbxEntity").trim If scbxEntity.Split(".")(0) = "" Then scbxEntity = sCube & ".base" If scbxEntity = "" Then scbxEntity = "ARMY.base"
Dim scbxScenario As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("cbxScenario").trim If scbxScenario <> "" Then sCube = "ARMY" sCurrScenario = scbxScenario iCurrYear = CInt(scbxScenario.Substring(5,4)) 'brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": iCurrWFYear=" & iCurrWFYear) End If
Dim iEntId As Integer = api.Members.GetMemberId(dimtype.Entity.Id, scbxEntity.Split(".")(0))
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": scbxEntity=" & scbxEntity)
Dim bEntIsBase As Boolean = Not api.Members.HasChildren(api.Pov.EntityDim.DimPk, iEntId, Nothing)
Dim sFlowMbrFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FlowMbr","Command_Requirements.Base.Where(Name doesnotcontain REQ_00)").trim 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sFlowMbrFilter=" & sFlowMbrFilter & " bEntIsBase=" & bEntIsBase & " scbxEntity=" & scbxEntity)
Dim sDimDef As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ReturnDim").trim Dim sTimeOffset As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TimeOffset").trim Dim sTitleSearch As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TitleSearch","") 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"{sDebugRuleName}.{sDebugFuncName}: sMode = {sMode} || sTitleSearch: {sTitleSearch}")
Dim sScenario As String = sCurrScenario Dim iYear As Integer = iCurrYear Select Case True Case sTimeOffset.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Prior2") sScenario = sCurrScenario.Replace(iCurrYear.ToString, (iCurrYear - 2).ToString) iYear = iCurrYear - 2 Case sTimeOffset.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Prior") sScenario = sCurrScenario.Replace(iCurrYear.ToString, (iCurrYear - 1).ToString) iYear = iCurrYear - 1 Case sTimeOffset.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Next") sScenario = sCurrScenario.Replace(iCurrYear.ToString, (iCurrYear + 1).ToString) iYear = iCurrYear + 1 Case sTimeOffset.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Next2") sScenario = sCurrScenario.Replace(iCurrYear.ToString, (iCurrYear + 2).ToString) iYear = iCurrYear + 2 End Select
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sScenario=" & sScenario & " iYear=" & iYear & " sCurrScenario = " & sCurrScenario & " sTimeOffset=" & sTimeOffset )
Dim lsAllREQList As New List( Of String) Dim lsMasterDimList As New List( Of String)
If sFlowMbrFilter= "Top" Then 'lsAllREQList.Add("E#[" & scbxEntity & "]:F#[" & sFlowMbrFilter & "]")
If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#") And sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("F#") Then sDimDef = "E#F#" & sDimDef.Replace("E#","").Replace("F#","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", sDimDef) Else args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#" & sDimDef) End If
Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#ARMY:S#" & sScenario & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U7#None:U8#None" args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": sDataBufferPOVScript=" & sDataBufferPOVScript) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Time", iYear & ", " & iYear+1 & ", " & iYear+2 & ", " & iYear+3 & ", " & iYear+4 ) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", scbxEntity) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", sFlowMbrFilter) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True")
lsMasterDimList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": lsMasterDimList=" & String.Join(", " , lsMasterDimList))
Return lsMasterDimList
Else '================================================================================================================================================== '========== get REQ return list ================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim SQL As New Text.StringBuilder SQL.Append("Select CUBE, SCENARIO, TIME, CONS, ENTITY, FLOW From DATAATTACHMENT Where ACCOUNT = 'REQ_Title' And CONS = 'USD' And SCENARIO = '" & sScenario & "' And TIME = '" & iYear.ToString & "'") If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sTitleSearch) Then SQL.Append($" AND TEXT LIKE '%{sTitleSearch}%'") End If 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": SQL: " & SQL.ToString) Dim dtRollFwdReq As DataTable
Using dbConn As DbConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) dtRollFwdReq = BRApi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConn,SQL.ToString(),True) End Using 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"{sDebugRuleName}.{sDebugFuncName}: dtRollFwdReq.Rows.Count = {dtRollFwdReq.Rows.Count}")
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== build REQ return list ================================================================================================================= '==================================================================================================================================================
Dim mbrEntityList As List(Of MemberInfo) = BRApi.Finance.Metadata.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, "E_ARMY", "E#" & scbxEntity, True)
If dtRollFwdReq.Rows.Count > 0 Then For Each drReq As DataRow In dtRollFwdReq.Rows '---- reduce list to only entities within filter ----- For Each MbrInfo In mbrEntityList 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"{sDebugRuleName}.{sDebugFuncName}: mbrinfo.Member.Name=" & mbrinfo.Member.Name & "drReq(Entit)=" & drReq("Entity") ) If Not mbrinfo.Member.Name.XFEqualsIgnoreCase(drReq("Entity")) Then Continue For lsAllREQList.Add($"E#[{drReq("Entity")}]:F#[{drReq("Flow")}]".ToLower) 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"{sDebugRuleName}.{sDebugFuncName}: E#[{drReq("Entity")}]:F#[{drReq("Flow")}]".ToLower) Next Next End If
'Check if loop output values 'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, $"{sDebugRuleName}.{sDebugFuncName}: lsAllREQList.Count = {lsAllREQList.Count}") If lsAllREQList.Count = 0 Then Return lsAllREQList End If
End If
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": lsAllREQList=" & String.Join(", " , lsAllREQList))
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== get REQs that have data based on Filters using General_Member_lists =================================================================== '==================================================================================================================================================
If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sDimDef) Then Return lsAllREQList Else
If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#") And sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("F#") Then sDimDef = "E#F#" & sDimDef.Replace("E#","").Replace("F#","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", sDimDef) Else args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#" & sDimDef) End If

#Region "GetAllREQListReapplyInflation" '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ' PURPOSE: return list of all E#F# requirements - searches data attachment table where REQ_Title is not blank ' ' LOGIC OVERVIEW: ' - SQL query against table = DATAATTACHMENT where REQ_Title is not empty ' - return list of E#F# ' ' USAGE: ' -Used to get All REQs for Reapply Inflation Rates calculation in REQ_Main_Calc ' MODIFIED: '10/3/24 - Created by JM '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Public Function GetAllREQListReapplyInflation(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As FinanceRulesApi, ByVal args As FinanceRulesArgs) As List(Of String) Try '================================================================================================================================================== '========== workflow vars ========================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim sCube As String = BRApi.Workflow.Metadata.GetProfile(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ProfileKey).CubeName Dim sCurrScenario As String = ScenarioDimHelper.GetNameFromId(si, si.WorkflowClusterPk.ScenarioKey) Dim iCurrWFYear As Integer = TimeDimHelper.GetYearFromId(si.WorkflowClusterPk.TimeKey)
Dim sTitleScenario As String = sCurrScenario Dim sTitleYear As String = iCurrWFYear.ToString
Dim lsEntity As New List(Of String) Dim lsFlow As New List(Of String)
Dim sEntityMbrfilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("EntityMbrFilter").trim Dim sFlowMbrFilter As String = "Command_Requirements.Base.Where(Name doesnotcontain REQ_00)" Dim sDimDef As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ReturnDim").trim Dim sMode As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Mode").trim Dim sTitleSearch As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TitleSearch","")
Dim sScenario As String = sCurrScenario Dim iYear As Integer = iCurrWFYear Select Case True Case sMode.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("Current") sScenario = sCurrScenario iYear = iCurrWFYear End Select
'================================================================================================================================================== '========== get REQ return list ================================================================================================================= '================================================================================================================================================== Dim SQL As New Text.StringBuilder SQL.Append("Select CUBE, SCENARIO, TIME, CONS, ENTITY, FLOW From DATAATTACHMENT Where ACCOUNT = 'REQ_Title' And CUBE = '" & sCube & "' And CONS = 'USD' And SCENARIO = '" & sScenario & "' And TIME = '" & iYear.ToString & "'") If Not String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sTitleSearch) Then SQL.Append($" AND TEXT LIKE '%{sTitleSearch}%'") End If
Dim dtReapply As DataTable Using dbConn As DbConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) dtReapply = BRApi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConn,SQL.ToString(),True) End Using '================================================================================================================================================== '========== build REQ return list ================================================================================================================= '==================================================================================================================================================
Dim mbrEntityList = sEntityMbrfilter Dim lsAllREQList As New List( Of String) If dtReapply.Rows.Count > 0 Then For Each drReq As DataRow In dtReapply.Rows '---- reduce list to only entities within filter ----- lsAllREQList.Add($"E#[{drReq("Entity")}]:F#[{drReq("Flow")}]".ToLower)
Next
End If
'Check if loop output values If lsAllREQList.Count = 0 Then lsAllREQList.Add("E#[None]:F#[None]") Return lsAllREQList End If '================================================================================================================================================== '========== get REQs that have data based on Filters using General_Member_lists =================================================================== '==================================================================================================================================================
Dim lsMasterDimList As New List( Of String) If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(sDimDef) Then Return lsAllREQList Else
If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#") And sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("F#") Then sDimDef = "E#F#" & sDimDef.Replace("E#","").Replace("F#","") args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", sDimDef) Else args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DimDef", "E#F#" & sDimDef) End If
Dim sDataBufferPOVScript="Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sScenario & ":C#Local:V#Periodic:A#REQ_Requested_Amt:I#Top:O#BeforeAdj:U5#Top:U6#Top:U7#None:U8#None"
args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Time", iYear & ", " & iYear+1 & ", " & iYear+2 & ", " & iYear+3 & ", " & iYear+4 ) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Entity", sEntityMbrfilter) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("Flow", sFlowMbrFilter) args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ReturnList", "True") Dim sIC As String = "" If args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.ContainsKey("IC") Then sIC = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("IC").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("IC", sIC) End If
Dim sEntityFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("EntityFilter").trim
Dim U1Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U1Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U1Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U1#Top"
Dim U2Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U2Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U2Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U2#Top"
Dim U3ParentFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U3ParentFilter").trim
Dim U3Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U3Filter").trim
If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3Filter) And String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U3ParentFilter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U3#Top"
Dim U4Filter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("U4Filter").trim If String.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(U4Filter) Then sDataBufferPOVScript &= ":U4#Top"
If args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.ContainsKey("ICFilter") Then Dim sICFilter As String = args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("ICFilter").trim args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("ICFilter", sICFilter) End If
args.MemberListArgs.NameValuePairs.XFSetValue("DataBufferPOVScript", sDataBufferPOVScript) lsMasterDimList = BR_GeneralMemberLists.GetFilteredDataRows(si,globals,api,args)
'BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, sDebugRuleName & "." & sDebugFuncName & ": lsMasterDimList=" & String.Join(", " , lsMasterDimList)) End If
Dim lsDimMbrs As New List(Of String) For Each x As String In lsAllREQList For Each y As String In lsMasterDimList If y.Contains(x) Then If sDimDef.XFContainsIgnoreCase("E#F#") Then lsDimMbrs.Add(y) Else lsDimMbrs.Add(y.Replace($"{x}:","")) End If End If Next Next
If lsDimMbrs.Count = 0 Then lsDimMbrs.Add("E#[None]:F#[None]") Return lsDimMbrs End If lsDimMbrs = lsDimMbrs.Distinct().ToList() Return lsDimMbrs
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region

Imports System Imports System.Collections.Generic Imports System.Data Imports System.Data.Common Imports System.Globalization Imports System.IO Imports System.Linq Imports Microsoft.VisualBasic Imports OneStream.Finance.Database Imports OneStream.Finance.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Common Imports OneStream.Shared.Database Imports OneStream.Shared.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Wcf Imports OneStream.Stage.Database Imports OneStream.Stage.Engine Imports OneStreamWorkspacesApi Imports OneStreamWorkspacesApi.V800
Namespace Workspace.__WsNamespacePrefix.__WsAssemblyName Public Class CMD_PGM_Utilities
Public Function Test(ByVal si As SessionInfo) As Object Try
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw New XFException(si, ex) End Try End Function
Public shared Function CheckFor_General(ByVal si As SessionInfo, entity As String) As Object 'If the FC is a parent, add _General Dim fundCenter As String = entity Dim wfInfoDetails = Workspace.GBL.GBL_Assembly.GBL_Helpers.GetWFInfoDetails(si) Dim membList As List(Of memberinfo) = New List(Of MemberInfo) Dim objDimPk As DimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "E_" & wfInfoDetails("CMDName")) membList = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMembersUsingFilter(si, objDimPk, "E#" & fundCenter & ".base", True) If membList.Count > 1 Then fundCenter = fundCenter & "_General" End If Return fundCenter End Function
Public Shared Function GetUD3(ByVal si As SessionInfo, UD1 As String, UD3 As String) As Object '====== Get APPN_FUND And PARENT APPN_L2 ====== Brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "UD1: " & UD1 & ", UD3: " & UD3) Dim U1Name As String = UD1 Dim U1DimPk As DimPk = BRApi.Finance.Dim.GetDimPk(si, "U1_FundCode") Brapi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "U1DimPk: " & U1DimPk.ToString) Dim U1MemberID As Integer = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetMemberId(si,dimType.UD1.Id, U1Name) BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "U1MemberID: " & U1MemberID.ToString) Dim U1ParentName As String = BRApi.Finance.Members.GetParents(si,U1DimPk, U1MemberId, False, )(0).Name BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "U1ParentName: " & U1ParentName) Dim U3Concat As String = U1ParentName & "_" & UD3 BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "U3Concat: " & U3Concat) Return U3Concat
End Function
#Region "Get Inflation Rate" Public Shared Function GetInflationRate(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal sCube As String, ByVal sEntity As String, ByVal sScenario As String,ByVal sREQTime As String, ByVal sAPPN As String) As Object
Dim sInfRateScript As String = "Cb#" & sCube & ":S#" & sScenario & ":T#" & sREQTime & ":C#USD:E#"& sCube & "_General:V#Periodic:A#PGM_Inflation_Rate_Amt:O#BeforeAdj:I#None:F#None" sInfRateScript &= ":U1#" & sAPPN & ":U2#None:U3#None:U4#None:U5#None:U6#None:U7#None:U8#None" Dim dInflationRate As Decimal = 0 dInflationRate = BRApi.Finance.Data.GetDataCellUsingMemberScript(si, sCube, sInfRateScript).DataCellEx.DataCell.CellAmount Return dInflationRate
End Function #End Region
End Class End Namespace
